The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Coughlan to reveal it all 

London: A court hearing in the case brought

 by Ferrari against McLarens chief designer was cancelled on Wednesday

 when Mike Coughlan agreed to tell the Italian Formula One team how he got hold

 of its design secrets. 

Coughlan, who was suspended by McLaren last week

 when documents were found in his house, agreed to provide a sworn declaration

 answering Ferraris

 questions. (AP) 




